User is looking for resetting the workflow condition history.

If the below condition is set on a transition to be checked, and the user has performed the transition from *New* to *Send to Review* then the condition fails and the user cannot proceed further to transition the issue. 

 
|Separation of Duties condition|Condition preventing a user to perform the transition, if the user has already performed a transition on the issue.|

 
{code:java}
Only a user who has never transitioned the issue from New to Send to Review can execute this transition.{code}
A feature should be available to reset the condition(history) so the user can proceed to execute the transition next time(passing the condition).

