According to cloud documentation: [https://support.atlassian.com/jira-core-cloud/docs/search-syntax-for-text-fields/] one should be able to escape `[` and `]` and use them in search. That is not the case.

Having two issues with summaries `test` and `[test]` and searching for either `summary ~ "test"` or `summary ~ `"\\[test\\]"` results in both results being found in both cases.

